    <string name="about_title">About</string>
    <string name="about_version">Version %1$s</string>
    <string name="about_description">Ozero is an aggregator of VPN and anti-DPI engines in a single app. It bundles several proven solutions for bypassing blocks: ByeDPI, AmneziaWG (WARP), URnetwork P2P and others. Pick a single engine manually or chain several engines — each link solves its own task.</string>


